"{\"uid\": \"harpersbazaar.my-fashion-paris-olympic-2024-team-outfits\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"From the all-American flair of Team USA to the grace and elegance of Malaysia's \\\"The Malaya\\\" collection, the athletes' apparel did more than just showcase their national pride - it told captivating stories of their diverse cultures.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 232, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 31, \"end\": 39, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999856740943, \"rank\": 7.702215227785797e-09, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 69, \"end\": 77, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malaysia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6108175842458163e-28, \"text\": \"Malaysia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malaysia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malaysia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We spotlight the best Olympic team outfits from the Paris 2024 Opening Ceremony, celebrating the creativity and cultural significance behind each look.\", \"from\": 233, \"to\": 384, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The kick-off extravaganza of theParis 2024 Olympicswas a tribute to the rich tapestry of cultures worldwide.\", \"from\": 388, \"to\": 496, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A riot of colour and style took centre stage as each country's fashion choices became a lively homage to its unique heritage.\", \"from\": 497, \"to\": 622, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This year's event was a powerful testament to fashion's remarkable ability to unite cultures and honour traditions on the grandest stage.\", \"from\": 624, \"to\": 761, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Let us take a closer look at the fabulous team outfits that stole the spotlight during this unforgettable ceremony.\", \"from\": 763, \"to\": 878, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A post shared by Polo Ralph Lauren (@poloralphlauren)    Ralph Lauren designed Team USA's outfits, which featured a classic and patriotic look with striped shirts, denim, and suit jackets in red, white, and navy blue.The designs are aimed to evoke a sense of American patriotism with a classic, Ivy League-inspired look.\", \"from\": 884, \"to\": 1204, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 901, \"end\": 918, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren_Corporation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Polo Ralph Lauren\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren_Corporation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren_Corporation\"}, {\"begin\": 941, \"end\": 953, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren\", \"score\": 0.9592375585782813, \"rank\": 0.042494626129884194, \"text\": \"Ralph Lauren\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren\"}, {\"begin\": 963, \"end\": 971, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999856740943, \"rank\": 7.702215227785797e-09, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1143, \"end\": 1162, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_nationalism\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.668512514001964e-22, \"text\": \"American patriotism\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_nationalism\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_nationalism\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A post shared by Michel&Amazonka (@michelamazonka)    Designed by Michel Choigaalaa and Amazonka Choigaalaa, Mongolia's outfits included long white pleated skirts, embroidered vests, and traditional deels.\", \"from\": 1212, \"to\": 1417, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1300, \"end\": 1308, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazonka\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Amazonka\", \"types\": [\"Q482994\", \"Q386724\", \"Q2188189\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazonka\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazonka\"}, {\"begin\": 1321, \"end\": 1329, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"score\": 0.9999999999868123, \"rank\": 1.2109877554059621e-11, \"text\": \"Mongolia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The designs included celestial drawings and animal symbols reflecting Mongolian folklore.\", \"from\": 1418, \"to\": 1507, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1488, \"end\": 1506, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Culture_of_Mongolia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mongolian folklore\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Culture_of_Mongolia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Culture_of_Mongolia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This blend of tradition and modernity showcases Mongolia's rich cultural heritage on the global stage.\", \"from\": 1508, \"to\": 1610, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1556, \"end\": 1564, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"score\": 0.9999999999868123, \"rank\": 1.2109877554059621e-11, \"text\": \"Mongolia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A post shared by Olympic Council of Malaysia (@olympicmas)    Malaysia's athletes are set to make a fashion statement like never before, thanks to the popular designer Rizman Ruzaini.\", \"from\": 1618, \"to\": 1801, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1680, \"end\": 1688, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malaysia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6108175842458163e-28, \"text\": \"Malaysia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malaysia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malaysia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The dazzling collection, aptly named \\\"The Malaya,\\\" draws inspiration from traditional Malay attire, featuring eye-catching ensembles such as the Baju Melayu Teluk Belanga paired with a songkok and sampin for men, and the Baju Kurung with headscarves for women.\", \"from\": 1802, \"to\": 2062, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1888, \"end\": 1893, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malay_language\", \"score\": 0.9666533360629479, \"rank\": 0.03447630981639921, \"text\": \"Malay\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malay_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malay_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The designs, in gold, olive green, and brown, pay homage to Malaysian heritage and symbolise aspirations for Olympic gold\\u200b        A post shared by JUST IN XX (@justinxx_official)    Justin Chou designed Chinese Taipei's uniforms.\", \"from\": 2063, \"to\": 2292, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2123, \"end\": 2132, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malaysia\", \"score\": 0.9712334153760117, \"rank\": 0.029368705097246414, \"text\": \"Malaysian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malaysia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malaysia\"}, {\"begin\": 2218, \"end\": 2220, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Super_Bowl_XX\", \"score\": 0.9998181633333345, \"rank\": 0.00018186973602567108, \"text\": \"XX\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Super_Bowl_XX\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Super_Bowl_XX\"}, {\"begin\": 2245, \"end\": 2256, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Justin_Chou\", \"score\": 0.9999911657204444, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Justin Chou\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Justin_Chou\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Justin_Chou\"}, {\"begin\": 2274, \"end\": 2280, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taipei\", \"score\": 0.9556971270582946, \"rank\": 0.04635589549583907, \"text\": \"Taipei\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taipei\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taipei\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It showcased hand-crafted flowers and elements representing the region's culture, art, and craftsmanship, emphasising sustainability and cultural pride.\", \"from\": 2293, \"to\": 2445, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A post shared by Canadian Olympic Team (@teamcanada)    Lululemon created bold red-on-red uniforms for Canada, incorporating sustainable materials and subtle references to the country's national colours and symbols.\", \"from\": 2453, \"to\": 2668, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2470, \"end\": 2478, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"score\": 0.8782862281263671, \"rank\": 0.1380224015766475, \"text\": \"Canadian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\"}, {\"begin\": 2509, \"end\": 2518, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lululemon_Athletica\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lululemon\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lululemon_Athletica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lululemon_Athletica\"}, {\"begin\": 2556, \"end\": 2562, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.9999999413303176, \"rank\": 3.484425248625175e-08, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The attire included jackets, pants, and skirts made from sustainable materials, with subtle nods to Canada's national colours and symbols.\", \"from\": 2669, \"to\": 2807, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2769, \"end\": 2775, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.9999999413303176, \"rank\": 3.484425248625175e-08, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A post shared by LeagueFits (@leaguefits)    Sudan's athletes rocked their signature black suits adorned with traditional patterns, eye-catching fabrics, and meaningful symbols that proudly showcased the nation's rich cultural heritage.\", \"from\": 2815, \"to\": 3051, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2860, \"end\": 2865, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sudan\", \"score\": 0.9999963985279744, \"rank\": 2.5074785321402354e-06, \"text\": \"Sudan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sudan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sudan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A post shared by Stella Jean (@stellajean_sj_)    Taking a cue from the rich tapestry of traditional Haitian clothing, Haiti's uniforms were a delightful fusion of vivid prints and patterns that celebrated the nation's rich artistic and cultural heritage.\", \"from\": 3059, \"to\": 3314, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3076, \"end\": 3087, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stella_Jean\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stella Jean\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stella_Jean\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stella_Jean\"}, {\"begin\": 3160, \"end\": 3167, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haitian_Vodou\", \"score\": 0.9992442317102062, \"rank\": 0.00070399650972788, \"text\": \"Haitian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haitian_Vodou\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haitian_Vodou\"}, {\"begin\": 3178, \"end\": 3183, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haiti\", \"score\": 0.9999999573301475, \"rank\": 2.5510884341241598e-08, \"text\": \"Haiti\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haiti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haiti\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These outfits were more than just clothing; they were vibrant expressions of Haiti's indomitable spirit and unwavering strength.\", \"from\": 3315, \"to\": 3443, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3392, \"end\": 3397, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haiti\", \"score\": 0.9999999573301475, \"rank\": 2.5510884341241598e-08, \"text\": \"Haiti\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haiti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haiti\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A post shared by Bermuda Olympic Association (@nocbermuda)    Bermuda's team showcased their attire, which included Bermuda shorts in national colours, blazers, and ties.\", \"from\": 3451, \"to\": 3621, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3567, \"end\": 3581, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bermuda_shorts\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bermuda shorts\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bermuda_shorts\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bermuda_shorts\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This unique style is a nod to the country's tradition and laid-back island culture.\", \"from\": 3622, \"to\": 3705, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"These costumes not only highlighted the distinctive identities of each nation but also brought colour and variety to theParis 2024 Olympic opening ceremony.\", \"from\": 3709, \"to\": 3865, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Featured Image Credit: instagram/@olympics    Biz of Re Sdn.\", \"from\": 3869, \"to\": 3929, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Bhd.\", \"from\": 3930, \"to\": 3934, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Registration No: 200801011046 (812334-M).\", \"from\": 3935, \"to\": 3976, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All rights reserved.\", \"from\": 3977, \"to\": 3997, \"entities\": []}]}"